        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>This gritty powder improves responsiveness but suppresses thoughts and leaves you weakened. The saving throw for addiction to scour is DC 30, and the addiction is virulent.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">A</span> Interact (Ingested, Inhaled)</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> <span data-pf2-check=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-dc=\"25\" data-pf2-traits=\"alchemical,consumable,drug,ingested,inhaled,poison\" data-pf2-label=\"Scour DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Fortitude</span></p>\n<p><strong>Onset</strong> 1 hour</p>\n<p><strong>Maximum Duration</strong> 6 hours</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Stupefied]{Stupefied} 2 and +2 item bonus to Reflex saves and Dexterity-based skill checks (1 hour)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Fatigued]{Fatigued} (1 hour)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Drained]{Drained} 2 and fatigued (1 hour)</p>"
